1
00:00:20,270 --> 00:00:23,356
Apa cerita awak selama ini, Eun-ho?

2
00:00:25,442 --> 00:00:29,279
Saya buka syarikat dengan kawan universiti
selepas habis belajar.

3
00:00:32,615 --> 00:00:34,284
Awak masih buat <i>kumdo</i>?

4
00:00:36,119 --> 00:00:38,496
Saya berhenti selepas awak belasah saya.

5
00:00:41,291 --> 00:00:42,876
Saya main kasar sangat.

6
00:00:52,844 --> 00:00:54,763
Saya tak keruan selepas awak berhenti.

7
00:00:56,598 --> 00:00:57,432
Berhenti?

8
00:00:58,558 --> 00:00:59,559
Apa yang berlaku?

9
00:01:02,103 --> 00:01:03,688
<i>Itulah cerita aku, ya?</i>

10
00:01:04,189 --> 00:01:05,023
Sebenarnya…

11
00:01:09,110 --> 00:01:10,779
Adalah sebabnya.

12
00:01:12,947 --> 00:01:14,657
Takkanlah tak boleh telefon pun.

13
00:01:15,867 --> 00:01:16,701
Maafkan saya.

14
00:01:20,413 --> 00:01:22,207
Awak buat apa sekarang?

15
00:01:24,209 --> 00:01:27,045
Saya penerbit komik web.

16
00:01:29,839 --> 00:01:30,757
PENERBIT KOMIK WEB

17
00:01:31,341 --> 00:01:32,342
<i>Kad nama?</i>

18
00:01:33,718 --> 00:01:36,387
Saya kerja di syarikat Naemo,
dekat Hapjeong.

19
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:38,681
Baguslah.

20
00:01:39,516 --> 00:01:40,892
Sesuai dengan awak.

21
00:01:42,352 --> 00:01:43,937
Ini kad saya.

22
00:01:48,066 --> 00:01:50,485
Penerbit Seo Mi-rae.

23
00:01:51,945 --> 00:01:55,907
<i>Ini kali pertama identiti aku di sini</i>
<i>sama macam dalam realiti.</i>

24
00:01:58,952 --> 00:02:02,747
Peliklah dengar awak panggil saya begitu.

25
00:02:20,807 --> 00:02:21,641
Dah sampai.

26
00:02:21,724 --> 00:02:22,892
Inilah tempatnya.

27
00:02:22,976 --> 00:02:24,227
STUDIO ARKITEK ES

28
00:02:25,228 --> 00:02:27,021
Jadi, inilah syarikat awak.

29
00:02:31,776 --> 00:02:33,319
Mari jumpa selalu, ya?

30
00:02:35,113 --> 00:02:36,739
- Okey.
- Mari saya hantar balik.

31
00:02:36,823 --> 00:02:39,450
- Rumah awak di mana?
- Tak apa.

32
00:02:39,534 --> 00:02:42,453
- Awak mesti sibuk. Pergilah.
- Hari dah gelap.

33
00:02:43,496 --> 00:02:45,331
Saya bukan 20 tahun lagi.

34
00:02:45,415 --> 00:02:47,792
Minum arak di gerai
sendirian pun saya boleh.

35
00:02:48,751 --> 00:02:51,379
Dulu pun awak minum
tak macam orang 20 tahun.

36
00:02:55,175 --> 00:02:56,634
Saya pergi dululah.

37
00:02:57,135 --> 00:02:57,969
Jumpa nanti.

38
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,641
Helo?

39
00:03:45,141 --> 00:03:46,100
<i>Helo?</i>

40
00:03:47,227 --> 00:03:48,228
Helo?

41
00:03:48,728 --> 00:03:49,854
<i>Dah sampai rumah?</i>

42
00:03:50,355 --> 00:03:52,607
<i>Saya nak pastikan awak selamat sampai.</i>

43
00:03:54,901 --> 00:03:55,860
Eun-ho?

44
00:03:56,444 --> 00:03:58,446
Macam mana dia boleh telefon aku?

45
00:03:58,947 --> 00:03:59,781
<i>Helo?</i>

46
00:03:59,864 --> 00:04:02,367
Ya. Tunggu sekejap.

47
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:11,209
<i>Pelanggan pelan asas dan ke atas</i>

48
00:04:11,292 --> 00:04:16,089
<i>boleh menghantar dan menerima</i>
<i>panggilan serta mesej selepas log keluar.</i>

49
00:04:16,172 --> 00:04:17,298
Gila betullah!

50
00:04:17,382 --> 00:04:19,676
<i>Helo? Ini nombor Seo Mi-rae, bukan?</i>

51
00:04:20,426 --> 00:04:21,928
Ya, Eun-ho.

52
00:04:22,011 --> 00:04:24,847
<i>Awak sedang buat apa?</i>
<i>Saya tak boleh lelap.</i>

53
00:04:25,848 --> 00:04:27,684
Saya pun dah segar balik.

54
00:04:28,184 --> 00:04:31,020
<i>Boleh kita berbual sampai awak mengantuk?</i>

55
00:04:31,771 --> 00:04:32,730
Marilah.

56
00:04:34,857 --> 00:04:36,651
Orang lain tak tahu filem itu.

57
00:04:36,734 --> 00:04:38,528
<i>Semua peminat seram tahu.</i>

58
00:04:38,611 --> 00:04:40,989
<i>Heronya orang kampung. Itu yang uniknya.</i>

59
00:04:41,072 --> 00:04:41,906
Betul.

60
00:04:41,990 --> 00:04:46,369
Hero filem seram lain selalunya
orang luar yang baru sampai.

61
00:04:46,869 --> 00:04:47,704
<i>Betul!</i>

62
00:04:48,371 --> 00:04:51,165
<i>Nak tengok wayang nanti?</i>

63
00:04:52,333 --> 00:04:53,584
- Wayang?
<i>- Ya.</i>

64
00:04:53,668 --> 00:04:56,921
<i>Jumpa dekat pejabat awak.</i>
<i>Saya akan ke Stesen Hapjeong.</i>

65
00:04:57,005 --> 00:04:57,839
Apa?

66
00:04:58,965 --> 00:05:00,550
<i>Awak tak selesakah?</i>

67
00:05:02,969 --> 00:05:04,178
Tak, bukan…

68
00:05:11,311 --> 00:05:15,815
Kalau awak setuju, saya tunggu di sana
selepas awak habis kerja esok.

69
00:05:26,743 --> 00:05:28,661
<i>Realistik tak terkata.</i>

70
00:05:29,245 --> 00:05:30,288
Okey.

71
00:05:31,581 --> 00:05:32,415
Okeylah,

72
00:05:33,416 --> 00:05:34,500
kita jumpa esok.

73
00:05:40,798 --> 00:05:46,554
EPISOD 5
BATASAN KESEMPURNAAN

74
00:05:53,603 --> 00:05:55,271
Maaflah terlambat.

75
00:05:55,355 --> 00:05:57,023
Saya nak buat kopi sekejap.

76
00:05:57,106 --> 00:05:58,191
Saya dah buatkan.

77
00:05:58,274 --> 00:06:00,276
Tapi dah sejuk sebab awak lambat.

78
00:06:01,402 --> 00:06:02,570
Terima kasih.

79
00:06:03,071 --> 00:06:06,157
Saya sibuk semak fail
sampai terlupa tengok jam.

80
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,241
Boleh kita mula?

81
00:06:09,035 --> 00:06:12,538
Saya tak suka karya ini.
Ia meniru komik yang dah ada.

82
00:06:13,289 --> 00:06:14,374
Saya setuju.

83
00:06:14,457 --> 00:06:16,542
Mana ada karya yang terlalu asli?

84
00:06:17,168 --> 00:06:19,337
Garisan dan susun aturnya amatur.

85
00:06:19,420 --> 00:06:21,339
Itu kita boleh tolong betulkan.

86
00:06:22,215 --> 00:06:24,592
Boleh awak betulkan plotnya
yang kebudak-budakan?

87
00:06:24,675 --> 00:06:27,929
Ada komik yang popular
walaupun plotnya kebudak-budakan.

88
00:06:34,102 --> 00:06:34,936
Apa?

89
00:06:35,978 --> 00:06:37,563
Tak, saya cuma…

90
00:06:38,523 --> 00:06:40,858
Komik apa yang awak maksudkan?

91
00:06:40,942 --> 00:06:42,693
Banyaklah. Awak pun tahu.

92
00:06:45,029 --> 00:06:47,115
Betul cakap awak. Ada banyak.

93
00:06:49,742 --> 00:06:51,577
<i>Apa masalah dia hari ini?</i>

94
00:06:52,995 --> 00:06:54,163
Kita rehat dulu.

95
00:07:09,762 --> 00:07:12,765
<i>Dah sampai pejabat? Selamat bekerja!</i>

96
00:07:13,516 --> 00:07:17,019
<i>Bila kali terakhir</i>
<i>ada lelaki tanya khabar aku?</i>

97
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:25,069
Awak nak keluar makan? Nak ikut.

98
00:07:25,695 --> 00:07:28,489
Saya ada mesyuarat.
Keluarlah dengan Kyeong-nam.

99
00:07:28,573 --> 00:07:29,490
Nak pergi?

100
00:07:30,825 --> 00:07:32,076
Kami pun ada kerja.

101
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,578
Selamat makan.

102
00:07:35,872 --> 00:07:36,706
Jom.

103
00:07:37,206 --> 00:07:38,040
Okey.

104
00:07:59,770 --> 00:08:01,314
<i>Kekok betullah.</i>

105
00:08:03,733 --> 00:08:04,734
Awak suka cinta?

106
00:08:05,818 --> 00:08:06,652
Apa?

107
00:08:06,736 --> 00:08:08,863
Saya tanya sebab kita juri genre itu.

108
00:08:10,698 --> 00:08:12,742
Saya tak suka.

109
00:08:13,367 --> 00:08:14,202
Samalah.

110
00:08:15,161 --> 00:08:16,287
<i>Peduli apa aku?</i>

111
00:08:18,706 --> 00:08:19,707
Awak suka apa?

112
00:08:22,210 --> 00:08:23,169
Genre seram.

113
00:08:23,836 --> 00:08:24,670
Kenapa?

114
00:08:26,339 --> 00:08:28,174
Sebab…

115
00:08:28,257 --> 00:08:32,803
Saya selalu lupa jantung saya wujud,
jadi saya suka apabila ia berdebar.

116
00:08:33,971 --> 00:08:35,640
Saya pun minat genre seram.

117
00:08:35,723 --> 00:08:37,558
<i>Tak tanya pun.</i>

118
00:08:40,394 --> 00:08:43,397
Tentu awak tak suka uruskan
<i>Dia yang Perlu Dikenal</i>.

119
00:08:44,023 --> 00:08:45,691
Ya, mencabar jugalah.

120
00:08:46,192 --> 00:08:48,152
<i>Sebab kaulah aku dapat tajuk itu.</i>

121
00:08:49,237 --> 00:08:50,071
Sabarlah.

122
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,838
<i>Sekejap lagi saya sampai.</i>

123
00:09:10,049 --> 00:09:12,301
<i>Jangan terburu-buru, nanti jatuh.</i>

124
00:09:22,728 --> 00:09:23,563
Eun-ho!

125
00:09:28,859 --> 00:09:30,444
- Saya lambatkah?
- Tak.

126
00:09:31,404 --> 00:09:33,030
Filem dah nak mula. Jom.

127
00:09:39,453 --> 00:09:40,746
<i>Jangan bunuh aku!</i>

128
00:09:46,711 --> 00:09:48,045
<i>Jangan bunuh aku…</i>

129
00:09:50,256 --> 00:09:52,300
<i>Tolonglah, jangan bunuh aku!</i>

130
00:09:52,967 --> 00:09:54,719
<i>Tolonglah jangan bunuh aku…</i>

131
00:10:19,493 --> 00:10:20,953
Nak bertih jagung?

132
00:10:34,050 --> 00:10:37,511
<i>Apa orang cakap?</i>
<i>Debaran itu bukan emosi tapi fizikal?</i>

133
00:10:39,972 --> 00:10:40,973
<i>Bahagianya.</i>

134
00:10:45,478 --> 00:10:46,646
Bersepah, bukan?

135
00:10:49,273 --> 00:10:50,691
Cantiknya.

136
00:10:51,192 --> 00:10:52,610
Semua orang keluar.

137
00:10:53,194 --> 00:10:55,321
Tengok-tengoklah. Saya ambilkan air.

138
00:11:14,215 --> 00:11:15,383
Rindunya mereka.

139
00:11:21,430 --> 00:11:23,516
Muda betul kita dulu-dulu.

140
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:26,686
Dulu saya tak tahu…

141
00:11:31,023 --> 00:11:32,608
yang saya takkan…

142
00:11:34,610 --> 00:11:36,028
lupakan awak.

143
00:11:43,536 --> 00:11:46,205
Bumbungnya cantik.
Nak ambil angin di atas?

144
00:11:57,717 --> 00:11:58,551
Kenapa?

145
00:12:34,545 --> 00:12:36,088
Nanti awak hilang lagikah?

146
00:12:41,051 --> 00:12:41,886
Tak.

147
00:12:47,349 --> 00:12:49,810
Saya takkan ke mana-mana.

148
00:13:01,655 --> 00:13:04,575
<i>Saya nak pergi kerja. Jaga diri.</i>

149
00:13:11,373 --> 00:13:12,875
<i>Nak makan apa hari ini?</i>

150
00:13:14,919 --> 00:13:16,712
<i>Saya belum fikir.</i>

151
00:13:16,796 --> 00:13:20,716
<i>Hari itu awak nak lasagna.</i>
<i>Saya akan cari kedai lasagna yang sedap.</i>

152
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:22,676
…mungkin itu satu faktor.

153
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:25,471
Betul, ia ada kelebihan tersendiri,

154
00:13:25,554 --> 00:13:28,182
tapi cukupkah untuk mengatasi kelemahan…

155
00:13:28,265 --> 00:13:29,308
Awak buat apa?

156
00:13:37,024 --> 00:13:37,858
Kenapa tanya?

157
00:13:40,319 --> 00:13:41,278
Tak ada apa-apa.

158
00:13:43,405 --> 00:13:44,532
Teruskan, ya.

159
00:13:47,326 --> 00:13:48,285
Eun-ho!

160
00:13:52,373 --> 00:13:53,624
Saya lambatkah?

161
00:13:53,707 --> 00:13:54,542
Awak cantik.

162
00:14:08,430 --> 00:14:11,767
<i>Masa lapang beberapa jam</i>
<i>selepas aku habis kerja…</i>

163
00:14:17,189 --> 00:14:20,109
<i>Akhirnya aku jumpa cara yang sempurna</i>

164
00:14:20,943 --> 00:14:22,361
<i>untuk luangkan masa itu.</i>

165
00:14:24,989 --> 00:14:25,865
Tengoklah ini.

166
00:14:56,979 --> 00:14:59,023
<i>Pernahkah aku alami</i>

167
00:14:59,106 --> 00:15:00,649
<i>janji temu seindah ini?</i>

168
00:15:02,234 --> 00:15:03,819
Seronoknya.

169
00:15:18,417 --> 00:15:21,253
<i>Pernahkah masa berlalu sepantas ini?</i>

170
00:16:24,483 --> 00:16:26,110
Janganlah menangis lagi.

171
00:16:32,241 --> 00:16:33,075
Hei.

172
00:16:34,243 --> 00:16:37,663
Minum dan lupakan dia,
atau merayu dia terima awak semula.

173
00:16:45,504 --> 00:16:48,215
Tak ada. Mereka langsung tak wujud.

174
00:16:49,508 --> 00:16:50,592
Siapa?

175
00:16:51,385 --> 00:16:54,513
Tiada lelaki mampu jadi
pasangan sempurna untuk saya.

176
00:16:55,055 --> 00:16:59,893
Kalau saya tak jumpa selepas 30 orang,
maknanya dia tak wujud.

177
00:17:01,687 --> 00:17:03,605
Habis, awak dah serik bercinta?

178
00:17:03,689 --> 00:17:05,941
Entahlah. Celaka betullah!

179
00:17:08,902 --> 00:17:10,738
Kenapa awak tiba-tiba mencarut?

180
00:17:10,821 --> 00:17:12,781
Buang masa saja!

181
00:17:12,865 --> 00:17:15,034
Kalau saya fokus pada benda lain,

182
00:17:15,117 --> 00:17:18,704
tak payah saya penat ajar budak,
walaupun ada ijazah sarjana.

183
00:17:18,787 --> 00:17:20,581
Mesti saya dah berjaya!

184
00:17:21,707 --> 00:17:24,793
Janganlah drama sangat.
Belum terlambat lagilah.

185
00:17:25,294 --> 00:17:26,795
Dah terlambat.

186
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:30,549
Saya dah habis tenaga layan lelaki.

187
00:17:30,632 --> 00:17:32,843
Saya dah tak larat buat apa-apa.

188
00:17:34,470 --> 00:17:35,304
Hei.

189
00:17:37,806 --> 00:17:40,559
Lagi untung kalau jadi awak.

190
00:17:41,310 --> 00:17:42,561
Menyesal saya

191
00:17:43,228 --> 00:17:46,565
tak hidup macam awak!

192
00:17:53,739 --> 00:17:54,573
Apa?

193
00:17:59,495 --> 00:18:00,537
JI-YEON

194
00:18:00,621 --> 00:18:02,873
<i>Hei, gambar profil saya cantik tak?</i>

195
00:18:02,956 --> 00:18:04,792
<i>Nampak tak saya pura-pura okey?</i>

196
00:18:06,752 --> 00:18:08,045
<i>Nampak sangat.</i>

197
00:18:08,545 --> 00:18:10,839
EUN-HO

198
00:18:11,965 --> 00:18:12,925
Helo.

199
00:18:13,008 --> 00:18:15,302
<i>Datang tak? Kenapa dengan kawan awak?</i>

200
00:18:16,095 --> 00:18:17,805
Dia baru putus cinta.

201
00:18:19,306 --> 00:18:20,724
<i>Kasihan dia.</i>

202
00:18:21,308 --> 00:18:22,392
Hei, Eun-ho.

203
00:18:22,476 --> 00:18:26,146
Wujud tak pasangan yang sempurna
untuk kita semua di dunia ini?

204
00:18:26,230 --> 00:18:28,482
<i>Tak tahulah. Kenapa awak tanya?</i>

205
00:18:28,982 --> 00:18:30,442
Nak tahu saja.

206
00:18:30,526 --> 00:18:33,987
<i>Mesti saya tak cukup bagus</i>
<i>kalau awak tanya begitu.</i>

207
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:36,406
Bukan begitulah.

208
00:18:38,367 --> 00:18:40,452
Cuaca dah semakin sejuk.

209
00:18:41,286 --> 00:18:45,207
<i>Sudahkah aku jumpa jawapan</i>
<i>yang dicari-cari oleh Ji-yeon?</i>

210
00:18:53,590 --> 00:18:55,008
- Eun-ho.
- Ya?

211
00:18:55,509 --> 00:18:59,263
Semasa awak bersama saya,
awak seronok tak?

212
00:19:03,058 --> 00:19:05,018
Tadi tanya dalam telefon,
sekarang ini pula.

213
00:19:06,103 --> 00:19:07,729
Peliklah soalan awak.

214
00:19:07,813 --> 00:19:10,649
Cakaplah, awak seronok tak jumpa saya?

215
00:19:15,070 --> 00:19:16,321
Apa awak nak tahu?

216
00:19:22,369 --> 00:19:23,954
Hubungan kita…

217
00:19:25,956 --> 00:19:27,332
baik, bukan?

218
00:19:28,333 --> 00:19:30,169
Betulkah awak

219
00:19:31,003 --> 00:19:32,629
pilihan terbaik untuk saya?

220
00:19:36,008 --> 00:19:36,842
Mi-rae.

221
00:19:40,179 --> 00:19:42,264
Saya gembira bersama awak.

222
00:19:44,266 --> 00:19:46,018
Semasa kita tak bersama,

223
00:19:47,352 --> 00:19:49,104
saya gembira fikirkan awak.

224
00:19:53,525 --> 00:19:55,277
Awak fikir tentang apa?

225
00:19:57,196 --> 00:19:58,238
Cara awak senyum.

226
00:19:59,615 --> 00:20:01,033
Cara awak jalan.

227
00:20:01,617 --> 00:20:02,701
Cara awak makan.

228
00:20:03,535 --> 00:20:04,953
Cara awak cakap. Semuanya.

229
00:20:07,915 --> 00:20:08,916
Jadi,

230
00:20:09,958 --> 00:20:11,210
buang rasa ragu-ragu.

231
00:20:14,379 --> 00:20:15,214
Okey.

232
00:20:16,840 --> 00:20:17,966
Kecil hati saya, tahu?

233
00:20:19,676 --> 00:20:20,510
Maaflah.

234
00:20:28,435 --> 00:20:30,145
<i>Ji-yeon tak jumpa jawapannya.</i>

235
00:20:33,565 --> 00:20:35,317
<i>Tapi aku rasa aku dah jumpa.</i>

236
00:20:44,701 --> 00:20:47,287
Kenapa awak ikut kami? Mana pasukan awak?

237
00:20:48,330 --> 00:20:51,833
Mereka nak makan susyi,
tapi saya tak boleh makan mentah.

238
00:20:53,418 --> 00:20:56,630
Saya suka awak ikut sekali.
Jadilah geng makan kami.

239
00:20:58,173 --> 00:21:00,759
Kamu semua pergi bengkel nanti, bukan?

240
00:21:01,843 --> 00:21:03,053
Bengkel?

241
00:21:03,553 --> 00:21:05,555
- Ya, minggu ini.
- Awak tak pergi?

242
00:21:06,890 --> 00:21:08,016
Tak.

243
00:21:08,517 --> 00:21:10,102
Saya tak nak pergi.

244
00:21:10,602 --> 00:21:11,728
Saya kena pergikah?

245
00:21:13,605 --> 00:21:16,942
Awak lupa apa jadi dua tahun lalu
semasa awak tak pergi?

246
00:21:17,025 --> 00:21:17,859
Apa?

247
00:21:20,362 --> 00:21:22,155
Jom makan barbeku!

248
00:21:22,239 --> 00:21:24,741
- Barbeku!
- Mi-rae, jom makan barbeku!

249
00:21:24,825 --> 00:21:26,827
- Masuk!
- Cepat, Mi-rae!

250
00:21:36,253 --> 00:21:37,337
Sesak sangat.

251
00:21:39,047 --> 00:21:39,881
Saya kenyang.

252
00:21:41,758 --> 00:21:45,679
Projek itu berat sangat untuk seorang.
Bolehkah dia buat?

253
00:21:45,762 --> 00:21:48,932
Penulis dah setuju,
jadi kita teruskan ikut jadual…

254
00:21:49,016 --> 00:21:51,393
- Cakaplah kalau nak bantuan.
- Selesai.

255
00:21:51,476 --> 00:21:53,395
Bos, boleh tolong tengok…

256
00:21:53,478 --> 00:21:54,980
- Ada lagi nak tambah?
- Tak.

257
00:21:55,063 --> 00:21:55,897
Bersurai.

258
00:21:59,318 --> 00:22:03,238
Eh, tak makankah? Makan sampai kenyang.
Anggaplah macam saya bayar.

259
00:22:05,741 --> 00:22:08,535
Bos, semasa bengkel itu, saya sakit perut…

260
00:22:08,618 --> 00:22:10,454
Pesan satu sakit perut untuk…

261
00:22:12,414 --> 00:22:15,208
Hantar daging rusuk ke sini!

262
00:22:15,917 --> 00:22:17,502
Mi-rae, awak di sini lagi?

263
00:22:18,628 --> 00:22:19,963
Lama tak jumpa.

264
00:22:20,047 --> 00:22:23,467
Bengkel itu bagus.
Sebab itulah saya tak berhenti kerja.

265
00:22:23,550 --> 00:22:25,802
<i>Perangainya begitu selama tiga minggu.</i>

266
00:22:25,886 --> 00:22:28,180
Dia merajuk lain macam.

267
00:22:28,263 --> 00:22:32,267
Sekarang dia dua tahun lebih tua,
jadi mesti dia merajuk enam minggu.

268
00:22:34,144 --> 00:22:36,188
Dulu awak pun tak pergi.

269
00:22:36,271 --> 00:22:37,606
Awak kena marah tak?

270
00:22:37,689 --> 00:22:39,733
Tak, saya selamat.

271
00:22:39,816 --> 00:22:42,027
Awak tak pergi kali ini?

272
00:22:43,070 --> 00:22:44,446
Awak nak pergi, bukan?

273
00:22:45,322 --> 00:22:47,991
Peliklah kalau saya seorang tak pergi.

274
00:22:49,242 --> 00:22:50,160
Saya nak pergi.

275
00:22:50,744 --> 00:22:53,413
Awak nak pergi bengkel dua hari?

276
00:22:53,497 --> 00:22:55,832
Dah buang tabiatkah? Atau awak bosan?

277
00:22:55,916 --> 00:22:56,875
Tak.

278
00:22:57,876 --> 00:23:01,838
Rumah ibu bapa saya dekat sana.
Saya jumpa mereka hari Jumaat.

279
00:23:01,922 --> 00:23:05,342
Tapi itu hujung minggu.
Luangkanlah masa dengan keluarga.

280
00:23:06,468 --> 00:23:07,677
Tahulah saya fikir.

281
00:23:09,638 --> 00:23:11,681
JJAMPPONG BERAPI

282
00:23:17,729 --> 00:23:19,481
<i>Setan betul.</i>

283
00:23:19,981 --> 00:23:23,235
Wah, segarnya bau alam semula jadi.

284
00:23:24,069 --> 00:23:26,405
Bangun! Berapa lama awak nak tidur?

285
00:23:27,030 --> 00:23:29,658
Sikitnya kamu bawa barang.

286
00:23:30,158 --> 00:23:31,952
Suruh lelaki datang sini balik.

287
00:23:32,035 --> 00:23:35,163
<i>Berseronoklah. Saya rindu awak.</i>

288
00:23:42,921 --> 00:23:44,589
<i>Okey, nanti saya mesej.</i>

289
00:23:55,225 --> 00:23:56,059
Helo.

290
00:23:56,685 --> 00:23:57,519
Hai.

291
00:24:01,690 --> 00:24:04,401
Eun-ju! Ambil gambar saya di sini.

292
00:24:04,901 --> 00:24:06,445
KUIZ RAJA KOMIK NAEMO KE-7

293
00:24:06,528 --> 00:24:09,698
Baiklah, ini tradisi syarikat kita.

294
00:24:09,781 --> 00:24:12,409
Siapa peminat komik sebenar?
Kuiz raja komik!

295
00:24:15,787 --> 00:24:19,416
Juaranya akan diberi peluang
untuk memilih hadiah

296
00:24:19,499 --> 00:24:24,296
daripada koleksi yang dibawa
oleh Pengarah Hwang!

297
00:24:24,379 --> 00:24:26,548
Semuanya edisi terhad, tahu?

298
00:24:27,132 --> 00:24:29,259
Tak berubah langsung.

299
00:24:29,342 --> 00:24:31,178
- Sejak dulu?
- Tiap-tiap kali.

300
00:24:31,261 --> 00:24:33,555
Baiklah, soalan satu.

301
00:24:33,638 --> 00:24:36,975
Dengar dialog ini dan teka tajuk komiknya.

302
00:24:37,058 --> 00:24:40,979
"Ini kali pertama aku cakap dengan lelaki.
Aku bakal ada pakwekah?"

303
00:24:43,565 --> 00:24:45,901
- Seo Mi-rae.
- Mi-rae lagi laju. Jawab!

304
00:24:45,984 --> 00:24:47,986
<i>I Want to Hold Aono-kun so Badly</i>
<i>I Could Die</i>?

305
00:24:48,069 --> 00:24:50,489
- Betul!
- Betulkah?

306
00:24:51,990 --> 00:24:53,074
Ingat nama saya.

307
00:24:53,158 --> 00:24:55,410
- Dia Pasukan 2.
- Soalan dua.

308
00:24:55,494 --> 00:24:56,536
Ini komik klasik.

309
00:24:56,620 --> 00:24:58,163
Dalam <i>Dragon Ball</i>,

310
00:24:58,246 --> 00:25:01,500
apa Kejohanan Bela Diri Dunia pertama
yang disertai oleh Tenshinhan?

311
00:25:01,583 --> 00:25:02,584
Hye-bin!

312
00:25:03,710 --> 00:25:04,544
Yang ke-37!

313
00:25:04,628 --> 00:25:05,504
Salah.

314
00:25:05,587 --> 00:25:07,672
Mi-rae. Yang ke-23?

315
00:25:07,756 --> 00:25:09,758
- Salah!
- Mesti lebih 30.

316
00:25:09,841 --> 00:25:10,842
Taklah.

317
00:25:11,343 --> 00:25:12,928
- Kyeong-nam.
- Ya?

318
00:25:13,011 --> 00:25:15,722
- Yang ke-22.
- Ke-22?

319
00:25:15,805 --> 00:25:17,432
Betul!

320
00:25:21,186 --> 00:25:22,020
Kyeong-nam!

321
00:25:22,103 --> 00:25:24,773
Dalam <i>Polar Night</i>,
Cha Dong-hwan masuk tentera udara…

322
00:25:24,856 --> 00:25:26,650
- Seo Mi-rae!
- Wah.

323
00:25:26,733 --> 00:25:27,817
- Ya?
- Lapan tahun.

324
00:25:27,901 --> 00:25:29,861
Lapan tahun, betul!

325
00:25:30,362 --> 00:25:32,864
Dalam <i>Villain to Kill</i>,
semasa Kwon Yu-ri dalam bahaya,

326
00:25:32,948 --> 00:25:34,533
pemilik hotel tolong dia dan kata…

327
00:25:34,616 --> 00:25:36,117
- Park Kyeong-nam.
- Ya?

328
00:25:36,201 --> 00:25:37,202
"Selamat pagi."

329
00:25:37,285 --> 00:25:38,537
Tepat sekali!

330
00:25:38,620 --> 00:25:40,956
Dalam <i>A Bona Fide Killer</i>,
anak Bona membawa…

331
00:25:41,039 --> 00:25:41,915
Kyeong-nam.

332
00:25:41,998 --> 00:25:43,542
- Ya?
- Kongdoli.

333
00:25:43,625 --> 00:25:44,543
Betul!

334
00:25:44,626 --> 00:25:46,294
Dalam <i>Theme Park of Death</i>, Baek Jin…

335
00:25:46,378 --> 00:25:47,546
- Seo Mi-rae!
- Ya?

336
00:25:47,629 --> 00:25:48,630
Tren Rolling Z.

337
00:25:48,713 --> 00:25:49,965
Betul!

338
00:25:50,048 --> 00:25:51,383
Ya. Dia betul.

339
00:25:51,466 --> 00:25:54,469
Dalam <i>Transfer Student at Apocalypse High</i>,
kakak kawan Geon-u…

340
00:25:54,553 --> 00:25:55,637
Kyeong-nam.

341
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:57,389
- Kelas 2-5.
- Betul!

342
00:25:57,889 --> 00:26:00,892
Dalam <i>Abandoned House Diary</i>,
berapa ketinggian Oh Seong-chan?

343
00:26:00,976 --> 00:26:02,102
Mi-rae.

344
00:26:02,185 --> 00:26:03,270
175 sentimeter?

345
00:26:03,812 --> 00:26:05,063
- Salah!
- Kyeong-nam.

346
00:26:06,731 --> 00:26:07,899
176.

347
00:26:08,650 --> 00:26:10,151
Betul!

348
00:26:12,279 --> 00:26:14,197
- Mi-rae.
- Kyeong-nam.

349
00:26:14,281 --> 00:26:15,782
Mi-rae, Arapara Garatus!

350
00:26:15,865 --> 00:26:18,076
Arapara Garatus, betul!

351
00:26:18,159 --> 00:26:20,078
Betul! Arapara Garatus!

352
00:26:21,121 --> 00:26:23,957
Seo Mi-rae jawab soalan terakhir
dengan betul.

353
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:26,918
Persaingan sengit
antara kedua-dua peserta!

354
00:26:27,002 --> 00:26:29,462
Sekarang, saya akan umumkan keputusannya.

355
00:26:29,546 --> 00:26:34,551
Kuiz Raja Komik Naemo
yang ke-7 dimenangi oleh…

356
00:26:40,140 --> 00:26:42,309
Park Kyeong-nam!

357
00:26:44,060 --> 00:26:47,897
Pasukan 1 menang!
Hebatlah, Park Kyeong-nam!

358
00:26:51,776 --> 00:26:55,447
Awak nak menang hadiah apa
dalam pertandingan cari harta karun?

359
00:26:57,907 --> 00:26:59,075
Nak balik awal.

360
00:27:02,329 --> 00:27:03,204
Sejuklah!

361
00:27:03,288 --> 00:27:05,081
Saya dah tak larat cari.

362
00:27:05,165 --> 00:27:08,126
Gila apa sorok harta karun
dalam sungai sejuk beku?

363
00:27:08,209 --> 00:27:09,377
Ada lipan!

364
00:27:10,837 --> 00:27:12,339
- Mana?
- Bukanlah.

365
00:27:12,422 --> 00:27:13,840
- Itu ranting.
- Telefon!

366
00:27:13,923 --> 00:27:15,592
Alamak! Dah hanyut!

367
00:27:15,675 --> 00:27:16,968
Alamak!

368
00:27:17,052 --> 00:27:18,219
- Habislah!
- Aduh!

369
00:27:18,303 --> 00:27:20,180
- Apa kita nak buat?
- Tolong!

370
00:27:22,265 --> 00:27:24,601
Dong-min!

371
00:27:34,235 --> 00:27:35,195
Sejuk gila!

372
00:27:35,695 --> 00:27:37,572
- Saya boleh.
- Redah saja.

373
00:27:37,656 --> 00:27:39,783
- Cepatlah! Di sana!
- Sekejap.

374
00:27:39,866 --> 00:27:41,743
- Cepat!
- Masuklah ambil!

375
00:28:26,037 --> 00:28:27,122
Terima kasih.

376
00:28:28,456 --> 00:28:29,290
Tak sejukkah?

377
00:28:29,833 --> 00:28:32,460
Ia terlanggar batu agaknya.
Skrinnya retak.

378
00:28:34,295 --> 00:28:37,173
Betul cakap awak. Saya baru beli!

379
00:28:37,257 --> 00:28:39,092
Saya nak tukar seluar.

380
00:28:43,138 --> 00:28:44,723
Hebatlah, Kyeong-nam.

381
00:28:47,225 --> 00:28:49,894
Awak okey tak? Ini telefon baru.

382
00:28:49,978 --> 00:28:52,397
Ya, saya okey.

383
00:28:53,356 --> 00:28:54,399
Okey sangat.

384
00:28:54,482 --> 00:28:55,567
- Apa?
- Okey.

385
00:28:57,986 --> 00:28:59,362
Okey, mari minum!

386
00:28:59,446 --> 00:29:02,574
- Nak minta lagu apa-apa?
- Minum!

387
00:29:03,324 --> 00:29:05,243
Tak apalah, saya pilih sendiri.

388
00:29:07,537 --> 00:29:10,790
Saya tak sangka
awak datang ke bengkel ini.

389
00:29:10,874 --> 00:29:14,461
Ibu bapa awak tinggal sini?
Mereka petani tembikai susukah?

390
00:29:14,544 --> 00:29:18,047
Park Kyeong-nam ada bakat jadi bintang.

391
00:29:20,592 --> 00:29:22,218
Janganlah mengarut.

392
00:29:22,302 --> 00:29:23,261
Awak pun nampak.

393
00:29:23,344 --> 00:29:27,432
Semua orang berdiri saja,
tapi dia selamba masuk sungai.

394
00:29:27,932 --> 00:29:31,227
Kemudian dia terus pergi.
Manalah perempuan tak cair?

395
00:29:31,728 --> 00:29:32,812
Minumlah.

396
00:29:39,903 --> 00:29:40,862
Saya nak <i>soju</i>.

397
00:29:40,945 --> 00:29:42,447
<i>Aku melangkah ke lorong</i>

398
00:29:42,530 --> 00:29:44,699
<i>Ke lorong</i>

399
00:29:45,784 --> 00:29:50,121
<i>Jantungku berdegup kencang</i>

400
00:29:50,205 --> 00:29:52,207
<i>Berdegup kencang</i>

401
00:29:52,290 --> 00:29:55,251
<i>Tirai kamarmu</i>

402
00:29:55,335 --> 00:29:57,378
<i>Tertutup rapat…</i>

403
00:30:03,635 --> 00:30:04,469
Seo Mi-rae.

404
00:30:05,220 --> 00:30:06,054
Ya?

405
00:30:09,265 --> 00:30:10,099
Apa?

406
00:30:11,851 --> 00:30:12,769
Itu air, ya?

407
00:30:14,896 --> 00:30:15,730
Ini?

408
00:30:16,481 --> 00:30:17,398
Ini <i>soju</i>.

409
00:30:19,067 --> 00:30:21,069
<i>Soju </i>rupanya.

410
00:30:22,445 --> 00:30:23,822
Saya tak boleh minum.

411
00:30:24,906 --> 00:30:25,740
Apa?

412
00:30:26,407 --> 00:30:28,243
Saya tak boleh minum <i>soju</i>.

413
00:30:36,292 --> 00:30:39,796
Ini pun <i>soju</i>. Air ada di sana.

414
00:30:42,257 --> 00:30:43,424
Terima kasih.

415
00:30:50,223 --> 00:30:52,892
Biar betul? Dia cepat mabukkah?

416
00:30:55,770 --> 00:30:56,604
Panas!

417
00:31:20,461 --> 00:31:22,213
Kenapa tak sepadan?

418
00:31:28,094 --> 00:31:30,221
Botol dan penutupnya tak sepadan.

419
00:31:30,805 --> 00:31:33,892
Awak pencari jodohkah?
Kenapa awak cuba padankan?

420
00:31:33,975 --> 00:31:37,520
Tak, botol ini sepatutnya ada
penutup yang sepadan.

421
00:31:39,647 --> 00:31:41,065
Hei. Tengoklah.

422
00:31:42,108 --> 00:31:43,735
- Tengok situ.
- Biar betul?

423
00:31:43,818 --> 00:31:45,945
Mustahil botol ini tak ada penutup.

424
00:31:46,029 --> 00:31:47,155
Hei, tengoklah!

425
00:31:47,238 --> 00:31:48,948
Eun-ju, tengoklah!

426
00:31:49,032 --> 00:31:51,576
Inilah perangai dia kalau dah mabuk.

427
00:31:52,076 --> 00:31:53,953
Kyeong-nam. Pergi tidurlah.

428
00:31:54,037 --> 00:31:55,955
Tak sepadanlah.

429
00:31:56,039 --> 00:31:58,374
Awak tak faham. Ia perlu ada penutup.

430
00:31:58,458 --> 00:32:00,251
Yalah. Aduh, beratnya awak.

431
00:32:00,335 --> 00:32:03,588
- Inilah sisi tersorok dia.
- Penutupnya penting.

432
00:32:03,671 --> 00:32:05,089
Mari sini. Hati-hati.

433
00:32:05,173 --> 00:32:08,259
Dengar tak? Tanpa penutup, buruk padahnya.

434
00:32:08,343 --> 00:32:10,803
- Ya, itu memang penting.
- Saya serius.

435
00:32:10,887 --> 00:32:12,597
Tidur, okey? Tidur.

436
00:32:14,015 --> 00:32:16,935
- Hei, nyanyilah.
- Ia perlukan penutup.

437
00:32:17,018 --> 00:32:18,269
- Nyanyi.
- Tak nak.

438
00:32:18,353 --> 00:32:20,271
- Saya…
- Jangan pegang.

439
00:32:20,772 --> 00:32:24,859
Nyanyilah!

440
00:32:24,943 --> 00:32:26,402
Nyanyi satu lagu.

441
00:32:26,486 --> 00:32:28,112
- Saya tak boleh…
- Nyanyi!

442
00:32:28,780 --> 00:32:33,701
<i>Namun akhirnya</i>

443
00:32:34,285 --> 00:32:38,957
<i>Aku menangis sendirian</i>

444
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:41,042
<i>Merasakan kesakitan</i>

445
00:32:41,125 --> 00:32:45,630
<i>Balasan perbuatanku terhadapmu</i>
<i>Sanggupkah kau…</i>

446
00:32:48,132 --> 00:32:49,133
Sekian.

447
00:32:51,427 --> 00:32:53,429
Saya tak tahu lagu itu pendek.

448
00:32:54,097 --> 00:32:55,431
Kyeong-nam dah bangun.

449
00:32:55,515 --> 00:32:57,934
Dah okey? Awak boleh sambung tidur.

450
00:32:58,017 --> 00:32:59,102
Tak jadilah.

451
00:32:59,811 --> 00:33:00,937
Saya sakit telinga.

452
00:33:01,020 --> 00:33:02,021
Telinga?

453
00:33:03,022 --> 00:33:05,274
- Dia sakit apa pula?
- Telinga dia?

454
00:33:05,358 --> 00:33:06,609
Hei, giliran awak.

455
00:33:50,111 --> 00:33:52,572
Aku dah larang dia bercinta
dengan orang sepejabat.

456
00:33:56,659 --> 00:33:59,370
Mi-rae, gembira tak awak ikut?
Seronok, bukan?

457
00:33:59,454 --> 00:34:02,373
Itu bengkel terbaik dalam hidup saya, bos.

458
00:34:02,874 --> 00:34:05,376
- Lain kali pun mesti datang.
- Mestilah.

459
00:34:05,460 --> 00:34:08,254
- Seronok, bukan?
- Jom naik kereta Kyeong-nam.

460
00:34:09,005 --> 00:34:10,381
Dong-min!

461
00:34:10,465 --> 00:34:13,342
Kami naik bas.
Bawa Eun-ju pulang dengan selamat.

462
00:34:13,426 --> 00:34:14,594
Naiklah sekali.

463
00:34:14,677 --> 00:34:17,597
Ya! Keretanya lebih selesa.
Dia tak kisah pun.

464
00:34:19,182 --> 00:34:20,349
- Jangan!
- Kenapa?

465
00:34:21,059 --> 00:34:23,394
- Masuklah.
- Cepat!

466
00:34:27,648 --> 00:34:29,317
Saya nak duduk di belakang.

467
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:30,234
Apa?

468
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:38,034
Nak naik tak?

469
00:34:41,496 --> 00:34:42,663
Nak. Okey.

470
00:34:59,597 --> 00:35:02,934
- Saya boleh turun di sini.
- Saya pun nak turun sekali.

471
00:35:05,394 --> 00:35:07,063
Jangan muntah dalam kereta!

472
00:35:07,647 --> 00:35:09,982
Keluar. Cepat!

473
00:35:12,235 --> 00:35:13,486
Saya pun nak turun.

474
00:35:13,569 --> 00:35:14,612
Rumah awak jauh.

475
00:35:14,695 --> 00:35:16,656
Saya boleh naik tren. Tak apa.

476
00:35:16,739 --> 00:35:19,492
Saya boleh hantar.
Saya memang ke arah sana.

477
00:35:24,455 --> 00:35:26,958
Jalan baik-baik. Terima kasih, Kyeong-nam.

478
00:35:27,041 --> 00:35:28,626
Jumpa esok.

479
00:35:39,846 --> 00:35:42,098
Sedap betul bau pewangi kereta awak.

480
00:35:44,016 --> 00:35:44,851
<i>Diamlah.</i>

481
00:35:44,934 --> 00:35:47,311
Awak berbau arak.
Awak terlebih minum agaknya.

482
00:35:47,395 --> 00:35:48,396
Apa?

483
00:35:49,480 --> 00:35:52,066
Mana ada. Betulkah?

484
00:35:55,319 --> 00:35:57,405
Boleh awak turun di Stesen Yongsan?

485
00:35:57,488 --> 00:35:58,322
Boleh.

486
00:35:58,990 --> 00:36:01,492
Tapi rumah awak di Seongsu, bukan?

487
00:36:01,993 --> 00:36:02,827
Betul.

488
00:36:03,619 --> 00:36:04,453
Habis…

489
00:36:04,537 --> 00:36:07,373
Saya ada mesyuarat dengan Hwany di sana.

490
00:36:07,874 --> 00:36:08,708
Hari Ahad pun?

491
00:36:09,500 --> 00:36:10,334
Ya.

492
00:36:12,170 --> 00:36:14,463
Saya ingat awak tak kerja hari cuti.

493
00:36:14,547 --> 00:36:18,009
Saya kena sokong dia
sementara dia bersemangat nak pulun.

494
00:36:20,219 --> 00:36:23,347
Dia bersemangat nak pulun?

495
00:36:23,431 --> 00:36:24,640
Okey.

496
00:36:25,141 --> 00:36:28,644
Apa khabar Cik Yun?
Bos kita nampak risau tentang dia.

497
00:36:30,313 --> 00:36:31,397
Risau tentang apa?

498
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:34,400
Jualan komik. Bulan lepas dah jatuh teruk.

499
00:36:35,651 --> 00:36:39,030
Itu cuma sebab Cik Yun cuti
dan ada promosi komik percuma.

500
00:36:39,113 --> 00:36:42,658
Rating komik dia pun teruk,
sebab itu bos risau.

501
00:36:44,702 --> 00:36:45,536
Okey.

502
00:36:45,620 --> 00:36:48,623
Nampaknya Hwany yang akan gantikan Cik Yun

503
00:36:48,706 --> 00:36:51,709
untuk buat komik pendek
yang pengiklan minta.

504
00:36:54,462 --> 00:36:56,047
Turun di situ boleh tak?

505
00:36:56,631 --> 00:36:57,465
Ya.

506
00:36:58,591 --> 00:37:03,262
Kenapa En. Hwang suka beritahu awak,
bukan beritahu saya sendiri?

507
00:37:03,888 --> 00:37:04,722
Entahlah.

508
00:37:07,850 --> 00:37:09,268
Terima kasih.

509
00:37:10,561 --> 00:37:12,813
Ada apa-apa lagi nak beritahu saya?

510
00:37:15,816 --> 00:37:16,734
Ada.

511
00:37:19,779 --> 00:37:20,613
Apa dia?

512
00:37:25,785 --> 00:37:27,203
Saya suka awak.

513
00:37:43,594 --> 00:37:44,428
Apa?

514
00:37:47,473 --> 00:37:48,391
Apa awak cakap?

515
00:37:48,474 --> 00:37:49,517
Awak dengar.

516
00:37:50,101 --> 00:37:53,229
Rasanya saya tak dengar betul-betul.

517
00:37:53,312 --> 00:37:55,481
Mungkin saya salah dengar.

518
00:37:55,564 --> 00:37:56,941
Saya kata

519
00:37:57,942 --> 00:37:59,610
saya suka awak.

520
00:38:01,112 --> 00:38:04,490
Apa? Kenapa tiba-tiba cakap begitu?

521
00:38:07,535 --> 00:38:08,536
Saya perlu gerak.

522
00:38:10,496 --> 00:38:11,330
Jumpa esok.

523
00:38:23,426 --> 00:38:26,053
Apa benda yang dia cakap?

524
00:38:37,481 --> 00:38:38,441
Mengarut betul.

525
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:40,943
Dia dah gilakah?

526
00:38:41,652 --> 00:38:43,654
Dia main-main, bukan?

527
00:38:44,864 --> 00:38:46,449
Lagipun…

528
00:38:47,283 --> 00:38:49,076
<i>dia dengan Eun-ju malam tadi.</i>

529
00:38:51,787 --> 00:38:52,997
Jantan gatal!

530
00:38:53,497 --> 00:38:55,416
Dia nak ada dua awek di pejabat?

531
00:38:55,499 --> 00:38:56,751
<i>Dia tak nak saya.</i>

532
00:38:56,834 --> 00:38:59,128
Saya cuma minat dia macam artis.

533
00:38:59,211 --> 00:39:01,505
Tapi malam itu saya dah mabuk.

534
00:39:01,589 --> 00:39:03,966
Alang-alang dia ada, saya cuba nasib.

535
00:39:04,050 --> 00:39:04,925
Apa jadi?

536
00:39:05,009 --> 00:39:06,302
Dia tolak mentah-mentah.

537
00:39:07,094 --> 00:39:09,013
Sakitnya macam kena tikam.

538
00:39:10,389 --> 00:39:13,142
Jadi, awak cuma nak saya tahukah?

539
00:39:14,393 --> 00:39:15,936
Cubalah fikir dulu.

540
00:39:16,020 --> 00:39:18,731
Kalau nak bercinta dengan saya.

541
00:39:19,273 --> 00:39:20,608
Rasa macam tak nak.

542
00:39:21,150 --> 00:39:22,276
Awak tak suka saya?

543
00:39:25,196 --> 00:39:27,114
Saya bukan tak suka awak,

544
00:39:27,198 --> 00:39:29,784
tapi saya tak rasa saya akan suka awak.

545
00:39:34,497 --> 00:39:37,583
Sekejap. Aduh, sakitnya kepala…

546
00:39:40,419 --> 00:39:43,547
<i>Aduh, dia memang tak normal.</i>

547
00:39:44,048 --> 00:39:47,259
Telefon rosak, hati patah.
Teruk betul bengkel itu.

548
00:39:48,219 --> 00:39:52,556
<i>Apa? Jadi, dia seriuskah</i>
<i>cakap begitu kepada aku?</i>

549
00:39:56,477 --> 00:39:57,812
- Sorokkan saya!
- Apa?

550
00:39:57,895 --> 00:39:59,313
Kenapa? Apa hal?

551
00:40:01,524 --> 00:40:03,609
Kenapa?

552
00:40:03,692 --> 00:40:05,069
Kenapa?

553
00:40:05,152 --> 00:40:07,571
Kamu kenapa?

554
00:40:07,655 --> 00:40:08,781
Kamu buat apa?

555
00:40:10,825 --> 00:40:12,159
Nak main kereta api?

556
00:40:12,243 --> 00:40:14,412
- Saya pun nak main!
- Jom!

557
00:40:19,917 --> 00:40:21,585
Sambung kerjalah.

558
00:40:23,504 --> 00:40:24,672
Saya suka.

559
00:40:28,467 --> 00:40:30,553
Pembaca pasti suka bahagian ini.

560
00:40:30,636 --> 00:40:34,473
Saya suka penghormatan yang dia selit
dan suka gaya seninya.

561
00:40:34,974 --> 00:40:37,935
Ia tak terikut-ikut trend
dan ada keunikan penulis baru.

562
00:40:38,018 --> 00:40:41,105
Kesimpulannya, pembaca pasti suka.

563
00:40:41,188 --> 00:40:43,524
<i>Saya suka awak.</i>

564
00:40:44,024 --> 00:40:46,444
<i>Kawallah diri!</i>

565
00:40:47,069 --> 00:40:49,155
- Boleh rehat sekejap?
- Boleh.

566
00:40:57,204 --> 00:40:58,831
Saya pun nak rehat.

567
00:41:04,462 --> 00:41:05,463
Tolak.

568
00:41:20,102 --> 00:41:22,021
Gila aku dibuatnya.

569
00:41:33,032 --> 00:41:34,617
<i>Hari ini pun tak jumpa?</i>

570
00:41:36,243 --> 00:41:38,913
<i>Kita jumpa nanti. Saya nak balik awal.</i>

571
00:41:52,718 --> 00:41:53,677
Seo Mi-rae.

572
00:41:53,761 --> 00:41:54,595
Ya?

573
00:41:55,262 --> 00:41:56,514
Saya buat salahkah?

574
00:41:57,932 --> 00:41:58,766
Apa?

575
00:42:05,648 --> 00:42:09,568
- Saya tak sangka awak nak lari-lari.
- Saya? Lari-lari?

576
00:42:09,652 --> 00:42:10,694
Bila pula saya…

577
00:42:11,529 --> 00:42:12,571
Boleh saya tunggu

578
00:42:13,447 --> 00:42:14,406
jawapan awak?

579
00:42:15,366 --> 00:42:16,534
<i>Alamak…</i>

580
00:42:17,034 --> 00:42:17,952
Atau saya patut

581
00:42:18,953 --> 00:42:19,995
lupakan saja?

582
00:42:27,545 --> 00:42:29,547
Sebenarnya, saya…

583
00:42:29,630 --> 00:42:33,008
Kalau awak ada teman lelaki,
cakap sajalah.

584
00:42:35,386 --> 00:42:36,720
Sebenarnya, saya…

585
00:42:37,346 --> 00:42:38,222
Saya ada.

586
00:42:41,433 --> 00:42:44,770
Saya dah ada teman lelaki.

587
00:42:45,521 --> 00:42:50,442
Jadi, saya akan pura-pura
saya tak dengar kata-kata awak.

588
00:42:51,694 --> 00:42:52,528
Okey.

589
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:54,154
Apa?

590
00:42:55,739 --> 00:42:56,574
Saya faham.

591
00:43:14,633 --> 00:43:18,429
<i>Dia pasrah begitu saja.</i>
<i>Kenapa semuanya mudah bagi dia?</i>

592
00:43:18,512 --> 00:43:20,347
Perasan bagus.

593
00:43:25,519 --> 00:43:27,521
PENERBIT PARK KYEONG-NAM

594
00:43:28,772 --> 00:43:31,025
<i>Entah apalah yang dia fikir?</i>

595
00:43:31,567 --> 00:43:32,526
Lantaklah.

596
00:43:58,385 --> 00:44:00,471
Jadi, awak bukan saja pandai <i>kumdo</i>?

597
00:44:01,305 --> 00:44:02,723
Saya serba boleh.

598
00:44:03,932 --> 00:44:06,769
- Saya nak meluncur sama.
- Cubalah kejar.

599
00:44:27,247 --> 00:44:28,082
Eun-ho.

600
00:44:29,583 --> 00:44:30,793
Ada orang suka saya.

601
00:44:31,877 --> 00:44:35,964
Lelaki yang buat awak serabut itu?
Saya dah agak pun.

602
00:44:37,007 --> 00:44:38,425
Macam mana awak tahu?

603
00:44:40,052 --> 00:44:41,553
Saya tak sangka langsung.

604
00:44:42,346 --> 00:44:45,557
Saya kata saya ada teman lelaki,
tapi dia kata, "Okey."

605
00:44:45,641 --> 00:44:47,685
Dia acah-acah mengurat sajakah?

606
00:44:47,768 --> 00:44:50,854
Dia nak cuba buat saya jatuh cinta?
Menyampah betul.

607
00:44:50,938 --> 00:44:53,982
Awak fikirkan lelaki lain
padahal awak dengan saya.

608
00:44:57,361 --> 00:44:58,862
Awak cemburukah?

609
00:44:59,905 --> 00:45:00,823
Tak pun.

610
00:45:02,366 --> 00:45:05,119
Mesti awak cemburu. Betul tak?

611
00:45:12,751 --> 00:45:14,086
Aku makin cantikkah?

612
00:45:14,837 --> 00:45:16,505
Saya suka awak.

613
00:45:24,304 --> 00:45:25,723
Laku lagi rupanya aku.

614
00:45:26,849 --> 00:45:29,685
Cubalah buat juga.
Mesti sesuai dengan awak.

615
00:45:32,896 --> 00:45:35,482
Orang patah hati saja buat begini.

616
00:45:38,527 --> 00:45:41,905
Saya dah lupakan dia, okey?
Saya tak patah hati.

617
00:45:42,740 --> 00:45:46,326
Awak kecewa lagilah.
Sebab itu awak belanja sakan.

618
00:45:47,453 --> 00:45:49,955
Saya nak bersedia untuk era baru.

619
00:45:50,038 --> 00:45:53,667
Rugilah kalau muka secantik ini
terbazir begitu saja.

620
00:45:55,252 --> 00:45:56,253
Apa-apalah.

621
00:45:56,336 --> 00:45:57,755
Hei, ini Seo Eun-ho.

622
00:45:59,715 --> 00:46:00,883
Apa? Nak tengok.

623
00:46:01,717 --> 00:46:03,761
- Kacaknya dia.
- Kacak gila.

624
00:46:05,471 --> 00:46:07,306
- Awak dah cuba yang ini?
- Dah.

625
00:46:07,389 --> 00:46:08,348
Memang seronok.

626
00:46:08,974 --> 00:46:10,476
- Yang mana?
- Yang ini.

627
00:46:11,059 --> 00:46:13,312
- Awak tengok Bima Sakti?
- Mestilah.

628
00:46:14,146 --> 00:46:15,898
- Saya nak cuba yang ini.
- Rombongan?

629
00:46:16,398 --> 00:46:18,901
Saya suka yang ini. Hujan tiba-tiba turun…

630
00:46:18,984 --> 00:46:19,818
CINTA PERTAMA

631
00:46:19,902 --> 00:46:21,779
Comelnya dia.

632
00:46:21,862 --> 00:46:22,696
Ini apa?

633
00:46:31,538 --> 00:46:34,166
<i>Seo Eun-ho menerima sambutan hangat.</i>

634
00:46:34,249 --> 00:46:37,211
<i>Dia baik tapi seksi.</i>
<i>Gagah tapi perlukan belaian.</i>

635
00:46:37,294 --> 00:46:39,922
<i>Saya temu bual para wanita</i>
<i>yang jatuh cinta dengannya.</i>

636
00:46:40,005 --> 00:46:41,757
<i>Ini kata K, pekerja pejabat.</i>

637
00:46:41,840 --> 00:46:43,467
<i>Realiti dah tak penting.</i>

638
00:46:43,550 --> 00:46:46,178
<i>Apabila kami dating</i>
<i>selepas saya habis kerja,</i>

639
00:46:46,261 --> 00:46:48,472
<i>rasa macam keluar dating betul-betul.</i>

640
00:46:48,555 --> 00:46:50,724
<i>Tak, perasaannya lebih seronok.</i>

641
00:46:50,808 --> 00:46:53,477
<i>Lima saat terbaik Eun-ho sebagai pelajar.</i>

642
00:46:53,560 --> 00:46:56,313
<i>Lima. Mengikat tali </i>kumdo
<i>dengan berkarisma.</i>

643
00:46:56,939 --> 00:46:59,691
Jangan beri saya peluang.
Lawan habis-habisan.

644
00:47:01,735 --> 00:47:06,240
<i>Empat. Semasa hujan tiba-tiba turun,</i>
<i>berlari berdua seperti dalam filem.</i>

645
00:47:06,990 --> 00:47:10,244
<i>- Tiga.</i>
- Awak cuma anggap saya senior awak?

646
00:47:11,203 --> 00:47:12,120
<i>- Dua.</i>
- Peperiksaan?

647
00:47:12,204 --> 00:47:14,873
<i>Hari meluahkan perasaan</i>
<i>kepada satu sama lain.</i>

648
00:47:14,957 --> 00:47:17,209
Saya tak boleh jawab. Sebab awaklah.

649
00:47:18,293 --> 00:47:19,962
<i>Satu. Malam rombongan.</i>

650
00:47:20,045 --> 00:47:23,715
<i>Saat romantik duduk berdua</i>
<i>dan menyaksikan matahari terbenam.</i>

651
00:47:27,386 --> 00:47:29,304
<i>Lima saat terbaik Eun-ho sebagai arkitek.</i>

652
00:47:29,388 --> 00:47:32,307
<i>- Lima.</i>
- Tetap cantik macam dulu.

653
00:47:32,391 --> 00:47:36,645
<i>Empat. Mengikat apron dengan lembut,</i>
<i>tak ubah seperti zaman universiti.</i>

654
00:47:36,728 --> 00:47:37,563
<i>Tiga.</i>

655
00:47:37,646 --> 00:47:40,941
Dulu saya tak tahu
yang saya takkan lupakan awak.

656
00:48:36,997 --> 00:48:37,831
Apa?

657
00:48:39,917 --> 00:48:41,084
Mana dia pergi?

658
00:48:46,924 --> 00:48:47,758
Terkejut saya.

659
00:48:47,841 --> 00:48:48,967
Suka tak?

660
00:48:49,051 --> 00:48:50,093
Nah.

661
00:48:52,346 --> 00:48:54,723
Kenapa beri bunga? Ini hari istimewakah?

662
00:48:54,806 --> 00:48:57,976
Saya tiba-tiba rasa
nak hadiahkan bunga hari ini.

663
00:49:02,898 --> 00:49:04,066
Awak tak suka?

664
00:49:06,568 --> 00:49:08,445
Suka. Terima kasih.

665
00:49:40,686 --> 00:49:41,687
Apa halnya?

666
00:49:42,729 --> 00:49:44,731
Awak senyap sepanjang makan tadi.

667
00:49:47,275 --> 00:49:48,402
Betulkah?

668
00:49:50,153 --> 00:49:51,029
Awak okey tak?

669
00:49:52,823 --> 00:49:55,242
Ya. Semuanya okey.

670
00:50:06,044 --> 00:50:06,878
Mi-rae.

671
00:50:09,965 --> 00:50:10,799
Ya?

672
00:50:15,012 --> 00:50:16,013
Saya takut.

673
00:50:25,147 --> 00:50:27,065
Takut awak tinggalkan saya lagi.

674
00:50:32,696 --> 00:50:35,407
<i>Lima saat terbaik Eun-ho</i>
<i>sebagai arkitek. Dua.</i>

675
00:50:35,490 --> 00:50:38,076
<i>Saya takut.</i>
<i>Takut awak tinggalkan saya lagi.</i>

676
00:50:38,160 --> 00:50:38,994
Tak guna.

677
00:50:43,707 --> 00:50:46,126
Maaf. Kita cakap lain kali sajalah.

678
00:51:04,895 --> 00:51:06,480
Saya ada buat salahkah?

679
00:51:12,360 --> 00:51:13,612
Bukan begitu.

680
00:51:17,074 --> 00:51:18,241
Tengok saya.

681
00:51:43,058 --> 00:51:45,811
<i>Satu. Menolak ke dinding</i>
<i>untuk memberi ciuman.</i>

682
00:51:45,894 --> 00:51:48,939
<i>Mendedahkan kehangatan</i>
<i>di sebalik kelembutannya.</i>

683
00:51:50,941 --> 00:51:54,111
<i>Ini dah melampau sangat.</i>

684
00:51:56,655 --> 00:51:57,656
Eun-ho.

685
00:51:59,741 --> 00:52:02,410
Awak tak buat salah.

686
00:52:10,919 --> 00:52:12,337
Saya yang dah berubah.

687
00:52:14,798 --> 00:52:15,966
Sekarang ini,

688
00:52:16,716 --> 00:52:19,136
walau apa pun taktik yang awak cuba,

689
00:52:19,970 --> 00:52:21,513
saya dah tak boleh layan.

690
00:52:23,140 --> 00:52:24,349
Apa maksud awak?

691
00:52:29,104 --> 00:52:31,606
Kali ini saya akan beritahu sebelum pergi.

692
00:52:33,358 --> 00:52:34,276
Beritahu apa?

693
00:52:36,695 --> 00:52:38,655
Terima kasih atas segalanya.

694
00:52:44,661 --> 00:52:45,871
Jaga diri.

695
00:52:48,039 --> 00:52:48,874
Tidak.

696
00:52:52,669 --> 00:52:55,755
Celaka betul.
Berani kamu kenakan aku begini?

697
00:52:57,507 --> 00:53:01,178
Baiklah. Cukuplah.
Aku nak batalkan langganan.

698
00:53:25,869 --> 00:53:26,703
Terkejut saya!

699
00:53:29,080 --> 00:53:30,081
Apa khabar?

700
00:53:30,665 --> 00:53:31,791
Kenapa awak datang?

701
00:53:33,418 --> 00:53:35,086
Cakaplah, apa yang tak kena?

702
00:53:39,507 --> 00:53:41,009
Awak tak suka Seo Eun-ho?

703
00:53:41,092 --> 00:53:43,595
Teruskanlah dengan lelaki baru pula.

704
00:53:45,347 --> 00:53:48,892
Awak datang sebab saya nak
batalkan langganan saya?

705
00:53:50,310 --> 00:53:51,144
Aduhai.

706
00:53:52,145 --> 00:53:53,897
Apa maksud awak?

707
00:53:53,980 --> 00:53:56,900
Aduhai! Mana ada.

708
00:54:00,445 --> 00:54:01,988
Awak nak batalkan?

709
00:54:03,990 --> 00:54:04,991
Entahlah.

710
00:54:06,159 --> 00:54:10,413
Beritahulah saya. Kalau ada masalah,
kita boleh selesaikan bersama.

711
00:54:10,497 --> 00:54:14,167
Kenapalah awak nak terus
ambil tindakan drastik?

712
00:54:18,672 --> 00:54:19,714
Cakap cepat.

713
00:54:20,465 --> 00:54:23,969
Seo Eun-ho ada berapa ramai teman wanita?

714
00:54:27,347 --> 00:54:29,307
Perlukah awak tahu?

715
00:54:30,392 --> 00:54:33,395
Ya. Saya perlu tahu.

716
00:54:34,854 --> 00:54:35,689
Baiklah.

717
00:54:36,940 --> 00:54:37,941
Nah.

718
00:54:40,026 --> 00:54:40,860
CHOI SI-WOO

719
00:54:40,944 --> 00:54:41,778
SEO EUN-HO

720
00:54:43,738 --> 00:54:46,157
12,432 orang.

721
00:54:46,658 --> 00:54:47,492
Apa?

722
00:54:47,575 --> 00:54:49,411
Sekarang ada 12,434.

723
00:54:49,494 --> 00:54:52,747
Dua belas ribu…

724
00:54:52,831 --> 00:54:54,666
Siapa suruh awak tanya?

725
00:54:54,749 --> 00:54:58,545
Maknanya dia cakap benda sama
kepada perempuan lain juga.

726
00:54:58,628 --> 00:55:00,755
Bukan sikit, dua belas ribu…

727
00:55:01,715 --> 00:55:02,549
Kenapa?

728
00:55:03,341 --> 00:55:05,218
Apa? Bertambah lagikah?

729
00:55:06,636 --> 00:55:09,055
Sekarang ada 12,45…

730
00:55:09,723 --> 00:55:11,558
Tak apa. Saya dah tak nak tahu.

731
00:55:13,310 --> 00:55:14,436
Jadi, maksudnya

732
00:55:14,519 --> 00:55:18,523
awak tak suka Seo Eun-ho bercinta
dengan perempuan lain juga?

733
00:55:19,733 --> 00:55:21,026
Ya.

734
00:55:21,109 --> 00:55:22,027
Bukan…

735
00:55:22,110 --> 00:55:24,446
Otak saya faham, tapi hati saya…

736
00:55:25,822 --> 00:55:29,367
Tapi apa boleh buat?
Kalau difikirkan pun, ini normal saja.

737
00:55:29,451 --> 00:55:31,745
Ini bukan isu yang boleh diselesaikan.

738
00:55:33,621 --> 00:55:34,664
Ada penyelesaian.

739
00:55:37,292 --> 00:55:38,168
Apa?

740
00:55:38,251 --> 00:55:39,711
Ia boleh diselesaikan.

741
00:55:39,794 --> 00:55:42,130
Ada padanan yang khas untuk awak saja.

742
00:55:42,213 --> 00:55:44,341
Macamlah lelaki begitu wujud.

743
00:55:45,050 --> 00:55:47,886
Bilangan lelaki dalam Boyfriend On Demand

744
00:55:47,969 --> 00:55:50,972
bukan 900, tapi 901.

745
00:55:51,598 --> 00:55:56,770
Kami boleh hasilkan satu teman lelaki
yang dicipta khas untuk setiap akaun.

746
00:56:00,106 --> 00:56:04,319
Apa maksud awak, "dicipta khas"?

747
00:56:06,237 --> 00:56:11,451
Kami boleh hasilkan teman lelaki
yang paling cocok dengan awak seorang.

748
00:56:11,534 --> 00:56:13,161
Gu Yeong-il.

749
00:56:17,290 --> 00:56:18,708
Gu Yeong-il?

750
00:56:26,383 --> 00:56:27,384
<i>Seo Mi-rae,</i>

751
00:56:27,467 --> 00:56:31,638
<i>sila jawab kaji selidik untuk mencipta</i>
<i>teman lelaki khas dalam BoD.</i>

752
00:56:32,138 --> 00:56:35,475
<i>Kami perlu mengenali anda</i>
<i>dengan lebih terperinci.</i>

753
00:56:35,558 --> 00:56:38,812
<i>Penampilan yang anda suka,</i>
<i>personaliti yang anda suka.</i>

754
00:56:38,895 --> 00:56:42,982
<i>Anda mahu memimpin atau dipimpin?</i>
<i>Semuanya akan dianalisis.</i>

755
00:56:45,276 --> 00:56:46,277
Okey…

756
00:56:46,361 --> 00:56:50,073
"Saya suka rasa tak tenang
bercinta dengan lelaki pujaan ramai."

757
00:56:50,156 --> 00:56:51,032
Tidak.

758
00:56:51,116 --> 00:56:54,411
"Saya suka lelaki yang sesekali seksi,
bukan sepanjang masa."

759
00:56:54,494 --> 00:56:55,703
Ya.

760
00:56:55,787 --> 00:56:58,915
"Saya minat lelaki yang buat,
bukan cakap." Mestilah.

761
00:57:00,333 --> 00:57:01,167
Ya.

762
00:57:04,838 --> 00:57:06,589
Tak habis-habis lagi.

763
00:57:07,507 --> 00:57:08,925
Berapa banyak soalan?

764
00:57:10,510 --> 00:57:14,472
"Gambarkan lelaki idaman anda
dalam 2,000 aksara"?

765
00:57:16,015 --> 00:57:17,225
Biar betul.

766
00:57:18,810 --> 00:57:20,437
Kenapa banyak sangat?

767
00:57:25,066 --> 00:57:26,067
Bagus sangatkah?

768
00:57:26,151 --> 00:57:29,946
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND 901

769
00:57:30,029 --> 00:57:31,865
<i>Gu Yeong-il ialah raja BoD.</i>

770
00:57:31,948 --> 00:57:33,366
<i>Hebatnya cita rasa saya.</i>

771
00:57:33,450 --> 00:57:36,369
<i>Penyelamat yang bantu saya</i>
<i>lalui perpisahan pahit.</i>

772
00:57:36,453 --> 00:57:38,163
<i>Mengajar saya cinta pertama.</i>

773
00:57:38,246 --> 00:57:40,748
<i>Melanggan untuk dia saja pun dah berbaloi.</i>

774
00:57:40,832 --> 00:57:43,460
<i>Saya tak sedar saya idamkan</i>
<i>lelaki macam dia.</i>

775
00:57:46,087 --> 00:57:48,089
PENGOPTIMUMAN

776
00:57:52,385 --> 00:57:54,596
<i>Pengoptimuman selesai.</i>

777
00:57:56,055 --> 00:57:57,974
<i>Aku tak tahu arah tuju aku,</i>

778
00:57:58,475 --> 00:58:03,605
<i>tapi orang yang menunggu di hujung jalan</i>
<i>ialah calon paling sempurna untuk aku.</i>

779
00:59:01,746 --> 00:59:02,664
Apa hal?

780
00:59:59,262 --> 01:00:00,847
<i>Pintu dibuka.</i>

781
01:00:01,347 --> 01:00:02,181
Helo.

782
01:00:08,646 --> 01:00:10,106
<i>Pintu ditutup.</i>

783
01:01:13,836 --> 01:01:15,254
Awak cari apa?

784
01:01:15,338 --> 01:01:16,756
Terkejut saya.

785
01:01:19,676 --> 01:01:22,345
Tak, saya cuma…

786
01:01:27,266 --> 01:01:28,101
Nah!

787
01:01:29,352 --> 01:01:30,353
Awak cari ini?

788
01:01:39,696 --> 01:01:40,530
Dah.

789
01:03:50,034 --> 01:03:51,744
Terjemahan sari kata oleh FZA

